  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/releases/tag/v0.22.0</id>
    <title>New release for Pocket ID: v0.22.0</title>
    <updated>2025-01-01T17:15:24-05:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>stonith404/pocket-id</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add warning if passkeys missing (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/commit/2d0bd8dcbfb73650b7829cb66f40decb284bd73b"&gt;2d0bd8d&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;allow first and last name of user to be between 1 and 50 characters (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/commit/1ff20caa3ccd651f9fb30f958ffb807dfbbcbd8a"&gt;1ff20ca&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;hash in callback url is incorrectly appended (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/commit/f6f2736bba65eee017f2d8cdaa70621574092869"&gt;f6f2736&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;make user validation consistent between pages (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/commit/333a1a18d59f675111f4ed106fa5614ef563c6f4"&gt;333a1a1&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;passkey can't be added if &lt;code&gt;PUBLIC_APP_URL&lt;/code&gt; includes a port (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/commit/0729ce9e1a8dab9912900a01dcd0fbd892718a1a"&gt;0729ce9&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Sponsors&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/gatesry"&gt;Ryan Gates&lt;/a&gt; thank you very much for your tip!&lt;/p&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/releases/tag/v0.22.0" rel="alternate"/>
  </entry>
